'''阿达纳大屠杀'''（{{Lang-hy|Ատանայի կոտորած}}，{{Lang-tr|Adana İğtişaşı}}）是1909年4月发生在[[奥斯曼帝国|奥斯曼帝国]]的{{link-en|阿达纳省|Adana Vilayet}}一場針對亞美尼亞人的屠殺。在[[1909年奥斯曼帝国反革命政变|1909年奥斯曼帝国反革命政变]]中，奥斯曼帝国的[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]在[[阿达纳|阿达纳]]对亚美尼亚[[基督徒|基督徒]]进行了大屠杀，并在全省范围内扩大為一系列反亚美尼亚人的大屠杀<ref>Raymond H. Kévorkian, "The Cilician Massacres, April 1909" in ''Armenian Cilicia'', eds. {{link-en|Richard G. Hovannisian}} and Simon Payaslian. UCLA Armenian History and Culture Series: Historic Armenian Cities and Provinces, 7. Costa Mesa, California: Mazda Publishers, 2008, pp. 339-69.</ref>。据报告估计，阿达纳省的大屠杀导致多达20000至30000名亚美尼亚人死亡 <ref>{{Cite book|last=Adalian|first=Rouben Paul|editor-last=Totten|editor-first=Samuel|editor2-last=Parsons|editor2-first=William S.|title=The Armenian Genocide|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=6XYp-z5aP4MC&pg=PA132|accessdate=28 August 2013|year=2012|publisher=Routledge|isbn=9780415871914|pages=117–56|archive-date=2019-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605194838/https://books.google.com/books?id=6XYp-z5aP4MC&pg=PA132|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Adalian2010">{{Cite book|last=Adalian|first=Rouben Paul|title=Adana Massacre|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=QS-vSjHObOYC&pg=PA70|accessdate=28 August 2013|year=2010|publisher=Scarecrow Press|isbn=9780810874503|pages=70–71|archive-date=2019-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190604082526/https://books.google.com/books?id=QS-vSjHObOYC&pg=PA70|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同時還有約1,300名[[亚述人|亚述人]]也在大屠杀中遇害<ref>David Gaunt, [http://www.seyfocenter.com/index.php?sid=2&aID=36 "The Assyrian Genocide of 1915"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.seyfocenter.com/index.php?sid=2&aID=36 |date=20150320040115 }}, ''Assyrian Genocide Research Center'', 2009</ref>。   

屠杀的根源在于政治、经济和宗教差異<ref name="wealth">{{Cite news|title=ARMENIAN WEALTH CAUSED MASSACRES|url=http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F70910F93C5A15738DDDAC0A94DC405B898CF1D3|date=April 25, 1909|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2020-09-18|archive-date=2012-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121003154355/http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F70910F93C5A15738DDDAC0A94DC405B898CF1D3|dead-url=no}}</ref>。阿达纳的亚美尼亚人被描述为 "有錢人"；除了屠殺，暴力事件還包括摧毁 "拖拉机和其他类型的机械化设备"<ref name="ShamefulAct">{{link-en|Taner Akcam}}. ''{{link-en|A Shameful Act}}''. 2006, page 69–70: "fifteen to twenty thousand Armenians were killed"</ref>。     

